{"TopicId":218377,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Dark mode inconsistency","CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-12T20:19:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-12T20:19:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI use the dark mode which is pretty cool but it\u0027s not yet finished as I can see.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst of all, the formatting bar icons are not adapted to the dark mode, some are impossible to see (black on black or gray on black):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022U7I8E2p.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u00226.00\u0022 height=\u002268\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/U7I8E2p.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSecondly, when creating a new topic, the background is white for some reasons (when we create a bug reports it works though):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022A97C2bj.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002227.25\u0022 height=\u0022231\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/A97C2bj.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame thing for the search option:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022vFpNPb5.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002244.00\u0022 height=\u0022379\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/vFpNPb5.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-07-13T23:17:42Z\u0022 title=\u002207/13/2023 11:17  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dakota","CreatedById":225122,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-19T20:47:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI addressed the editor styling by just making it white. For some reason the buttons are colored pngs instead of svgs which could easily be stylized.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoth the topic background and search background have been addressed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-19T21:10:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224304076\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022218377\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689799620\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225122\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dakota\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, Dakota said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI addressed the editor styling by just making it white. For some reason the buttons are colored pngs instead of svgs which could easily be stylized.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoth the topic background and search background have been addressed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks a lot\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a bit out of place for the editor but it\u0027s a lot better than before, thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-01T08:55:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpeaking of the editor, why do the \u0022font\u0022 and \u0022size\u0022 buttons change their width when hovering above them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-01T16:11:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224307656\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022218377\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221690880152\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nazalassa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Nazalassa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpeaking of the editor, why do the \u0022font\u0022 and \u0022size\u0022 buttons change their width when hovering above them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey fluff up to appear larger when confronted with their natural predator, the cursor. \u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}